    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Medium model risk and Medium decision consequence. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and accepted on the basis that the ASTM F1717 protocol is standardized, inter-laboratory reproducibility is confirmed, and the clinical risk does not warrant additional loading conditions for this submission. The FEA ensemble demonstrates consistent predictive accuracy across all three QoIs at both laboratories. Credibility sufficient for regulatory submission.",
